{"tid":113724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【恐洩私隱】外國人前往強國 明起要留底指紋","createTime":"2017-02-09T08:08:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-10T10:38:53.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d7c9148cd255659df2d74831a2fbe91cd9f04047","tid":113724,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T08:08:16.000Z","msg":"2017-02-09 15:26:00 HKT<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國公安部今天宣布，為加強出入境管理，將對入境的14至70歲外國人留存指紋，明日起實施。第一批實施的將會在包括深圳機場等口岸，之後分批擴大實施。<br />\n<br />\n公安部透過網站宣布這消息，並指這項作法是根據「出境入境管理法」規定，並經國務院批准。<br />\n<br />\n公告指出，口岸將在今年內，陸續向14至70歲的外國人留存指紋，但持外交護照或有對等互惠安排的外國人，則可免留指紋。<br />\n<br />\n公安部宣稱，留存入境者的生物識別訊息，是「加強出入境管理的重要舉措」，且國際上已有多個國家實施這一措施。<br />\n<br />\n然而，深圳的口岸早在2005年已經開通旅客自助過關系統，港人在系統留下指紋、掃描面相後，便能自助過關。　<br />\n<br />\n公安部網站"},{"pid":"c6965a42a1d6856a27c22b62184282f68f414d86","tid":113724,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T08:14:05.000Z","msg":"證明香港係外國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de63f11e6544424ddbc1777a4acf6289f5ca59ba","tid":113724,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T08:16:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>證明香港係外國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做咩呀你"},{"pid":"ad94dc4cf8054d5b0c8a798726b78deb8d47cc38","tid":113724,"uid":80682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T08:19:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>證明香港係外國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做咩呀你</blockquote><br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"392477d2e10ea8a58bcbdd90d4233daa12f26764","tid":113724,"uid":35911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T08:28:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>證明香港係外國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"